Introducing GPT-5.5

Codex can now use GPT-5.5, OpenAI's newest frontier model for complex coding and professional work. It supports the same API features as GPT-5.4, including hosted tools, tool search, compaction, and phase handling.

Learn more: https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/latest-model

You can keep using your current model if you prefer.
